                    agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the service.
                </p>

                <section aria-labelledby="what-mytalli-is">
                    <h2 id="what-mytalli-is">What MyTalli is</h2>
                    <p>
                        MyTalli is a revenue dashboard. It connects to platforms you already use —
                        Stripe, Etsy, Gumroad, PayPal, Shopify — and shows you the data they make
                        available, in one place. It also lets you record manual revenue, expenses, and
                        payouts that aren't tied to a connected platform.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        MyTalli is <strong>not</strong> a payment processor, a tax advisor, an
                        accountant, an auditor, or a financial advisor. The data we display is read
                        from third-party platforms; we display it as accurately as we can but do not
                        guarantee it. Decisions you make based on that data are your own.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="eligibility">
                    <h2 id="eligibility">Eligibility</h2>
                    <p>
                        You must be at least 18 years old to use MyTalli. If you connect a platform on
                        behalf of a business, you represent that you have the authority to bind that
                        business to these terms.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="account">
                    <h2 id="account">Your account</h2>
                    <p>
                        You sign in with Google, Apple, or Microsoft. We do not store your password —
                        keeping your sign-in provider account secure is your responsibility. One
                        account per person; do not share an account.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        You are responsible for the activity on your account. If you suspect
                        unauthorized access, email
                        <a href="mailto:hello@mytalli.com">hello@mytalli.com</a> immediately.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="connected-platforms">
                    <h2 id="connected-platforms">Connected platforms</h2>
                    <p>
                        When you connect a platform, you authorize MyTalli to read sales, fees, and
                        payout data from your account on that platform. We do not write back —
                        MyTalli will never create, edit, or delete anything on a connected platform.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Each connected platform has its own terms of service that you remain bound by.
                        We are not responsible for the accuracy, availability, or behavior of those
                        platforms. If a platform changes or removes its API, your data may stop
                        syncing through no fault of ours. You can pause or disconnect any platform
                        from the Platforms page at any time.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="subscriptions">
                    <h2 id="subscriptions">Subscriptions and billing</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The free tier is available indefinitely with the limits stated on the pricing page.</li>
                        <li>Paid plans renew automatically at the price and interval shown at checkout. Stripe handles all billing.</li>
                        <li>You can cancel any time from My Plan. Your access continues until the end of the period you've already paid for.</li>
                        <li>Charges are non-refundable except where required by law. We do not pro-rate refunds for partial periods.</li>
                        <li>We may change pricing or plan limits with at least 30 days' notice by email. If you don't accept the change, you can cancel before it takes effect.</li>
                        <li>If a payment fails, we will retry through Stripe and may pause Pro features until the issue is resolved.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="acceptable-use">
                    <h2 id="acceptable-use">Acceptable use</h2>
                    <p>You agree not to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Use MyTalli to facilitate any illegal activity or to launder funds.</li>
                        <li>Reverse engineer, scrape, or attempt to extract data from MyTalli except through features we provide (such as CSV export).</li>
                        <li>Probe, attack, overload, or otherwise interfere with the service.</li>
                        <li>Use MyTalli to store data that does not belong to you or that you do not have authority to process.</li>
                        <li>Resell or sublicense access to MyTalli without our written permission.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these rules, with or without
                        notice depending on the severity.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section aria-labelledby="your-content">
                    <h2 id="your-content">Your content</h2>
